Cost-Optimization-Using-Lambda folder has the Python code to deploy it using the Lambda function 

CloudOptimizationPolicy.json - is the policy 
Lambda-function-to-delete-idel-instance.py - is the Python code which will delete the idle instances (CPU usage less than 10%)
------------------------------------------------------------
Downsizing underutilized instance:
Lambda-function-downsize-underutilized-Instances.py - is the Python code to downsize the underutilized instances mainly from t2.medium to t2.micro

IAM-additional-permission-downsize-underutilized-Instances.json - is the additional IAM role which needs to be added


